propertyTitle: L-Shaped House for Sale in Lafto

description:
If you are looking for a solidly built beautiful family residence, look no further. This is a thoughtfully designed home by South African architects and a lot of beautiful natural stones were used in the construction of the house. The house sits on Yeka Mountains, where you get breathtaking view of Addis Ababa and the Yerer Mountain Range. You have an amazing view even from “the basement,” which doesn’t feel like a basement at all.
It it is located away from all the hustle and bustle of downtown Addis. The other advantage of living in this neighborhood is that the air quality is much better than anywhere in the city. No wonder why all the big Ethiopian athletes train in this area.
Below is the distribution of the space:
Basement: kitchen, guest bedroom, properly made jacuzzi (the construction of the jacuzzi has cost 1.5 Million Birr), steam, sauna, gym, balcony with great view
Ground floor: living room, big open kitchen, restroom, spacious balcony with amazing view
1st Floor: Spacious Master bedroom, master bathroom with jacuzzi and shower, big walk-in closet, 2 other bedrooms with a shared bathroom, landing area with great view
2nd Floor: 2 bedrooms with a shared bathroom, a second living room with breathtaking view, open kitchen, big terrace with amazing view
There is covered parking for two cars and you can also park up to 6 cars in front of the house
Rear Side: Nice matured Garden, big space for vegetable garden, hand wash basin, maid’s room/bathroom, laundry room, storage room, traditional kitchen

propertyTitle: Villa for Sale in Summit

description:
Brand new building off Bole road, less than 5 minutes from the airport

● Grade A for Ethiopian standards

● Only 2 floors left

●Each floor is 653 m2

● Landlord prefers to rent a whole floor to a single tenant

● The smallest size one can rent is 325 m2

● There are 4 restrooms and 2 unirals on each floor

● One regular staircase + an emergency exit

● Fire hause available on each floor

● CCTV camera on every floor and access points to the building

● Building management on site

● Offices only (no retail space)

● companies like Voice of America and the MasterCard Foundation have taken space in the building

● You will have achance to choose from 3 types of floor tiles

● Tenant is responsible to do partitions

● Dedicated parks: 2 – 3 cars

● Total number of parking spaces: about 150 cars

● Garbage shoot

● Fiber optic connection

● Rent 590 ET Birr including VAT

● Common Area cleaning and security are taken care of by the management

● They may install smoke detectors

● No sprinklers (not common in Ethiopia)

● Photos are attached

● The photos showing the fitted out space are the office of the management. I included them so that you get an idea how the space looks like when finished

● The other photos show how the available space looks like at the moment. The landlord can do the floors in less than a month and handover to the tenant

● The spaces are being taken very quickly and I don’t expect the remaining spaces to stay available much longer due to shortage of good office space

propertyTitle: Simple and Beautifully Furnished Apartment in Cazanchis

description:
This 7 story Hotel consisting of 44 rooms is conveniently located in Hayahulet Mazoria, which is only 5 minutes drive from Bole International Airport and 3 minuets to Mesqel Square.
The hotel is solidly built and has a huge potential to become a very delightful place. With some renovation done, it will definitely make a thriving business and slaughter the competition very easily. The rooms are very spacious and most of them come with a big bathroom, sitting area and small kitchen. One of the big advantages this hotel offers is a huge parking space it has at the back. It is well known fact that even most 5 star hotels in Addis lack good parking and it is one of the primary causes of dissatisfaction of customers.
The hotel consists of the following:
*44 rooms (standard, king, double, suites, and family rooms)
*big kitchen connected to food and beverage elevator
*restaurant with nice street view
*laundry room
*business center with bathroom attached to it
*finance and admin offices
*staff rooms and cafeteria
*supervisor’s office
*office for the general manager
*spacious lobby with bar and cafe
*3 conference rooms with capacity of hosting 25, 40 and 150 people
*Nice terraces and balconies with nice view
*Parking for at least 40 cars
*great Mountain View of Yeka and Entoto
*handicap/will chair access
*elevator
*water tankers
*generator
Call +251911088114 to arrange a visit.

propertyTitle: Villa for Rent in Bole Area

description:
General Description about the development

We are pleased to offer you to live in our aesthetically planned and luxurious apartments included in our real estate project on CMC road. Our ten block apartments have two types of building designs sharing common compound gate. Each block has five floors and two floor penthouse with two luxuriously wide elevators. The spacious car parking situated in the basement of the apartments gives ample space for proprietors to use. As there is no driveway around the buildings, there is a high safety for children to enjoy bike riding and everyone to walk through the large gardens with a calm and pedestrian friendly environment.
The apartments have modern luxury feature creating new-generation living environments to make life convenient and comfortable. Besides, it gives a resort living impression with these wonderfully designed apartments looking over the peaceful compound.
The flats can only be accessed by modern security systems and the stairs are located away from the passenger elevators.Each floor has four flats,on each wing,consisting of 3-bedroom, 2-bedroom and 1-bedroom type apartments.

Features
•Located in the residential area on CMC road
•Gated compound with a courtyard for community events
•Fully finished apartments
•Underground parking
•Convenient transportation, nearby railway station
•Proximity to shopping centers, schools, health and recreational centers
Common facilities :
•swimming pool,
•fitness center,
•cafes,
•laundry,
•supermarket,
•multipurpose hall andrestaurant
•Electricity backed up by a generator
•Security camera in designated areas
•TV and Internet facilities supported by modern technology
Spaces available for common uses :
•Car washing
•Slaughtering
•Open traditional cooking area

Essentials
City – Addis Ababa
Area – CMC Road (Gurd shola)
Type – Apartment (G+7)
Essentials
City – Addis Ababa
Area – CMC Road (Gurd shola)
Type –Apartment
Bedrooms –3bedrooms
Bathrooms – 2(1ensuite)
Toilets –1 toilets

More Detailed Description of the 3 bedroom apartments
These spacious and well-designed 3-bedroom apartments are dream homes in a high-end community. The entryway with a corridor will lead you to an entrance of a generously sized living and dining room with plenty of natural light through two large French windows and a door connected to a large balcony that have a spectacular view to the compound.
